25|$|Malta {{requires}} twice yearly {{testing for}} Legionella bacteria at <b>cooling</b> <b>towers</b> and water fountains. Malta prohibits {{the installation of}} new <b>cooling</b> <b>towers</b> and evaporative condensers at health care facilities and schools.|$|R
